@startuml
[*] --> Start :
Start --> ChooseAmount : choose or enter a withdrawal amount
ChooseAmount --> SelectPredefinedAmount : support predefined amounts for selection by the user
SelectPredefinedAmount --> InputCustomAmount : allow users to input their own custom withdrawal amount
InputCustomAmount --> ConfirmTransaction : provide an option for the user to confirm the transaction
ConfirmTransaction --> CancelTransaction : provide an option for the user to cancel the transaction at any point
CancelTransaction --> ReturnCard : support if the user cancels the transaction, the system shall stop the transaction and return the card

@enduml
